# Extraccion de muestras

Muestra 1

muestra1 <- sample(u,100,replace = FALSE)
plot (muestra1, main="Muestra de tamaño 100",
     xlab="Elemntos de la muestra",
     ylab="uniformes(0,1)",
     col="blue")

### Histograma

hist(u,col=rainbow(15,0.23))

hist(muestra1,col=rainbow(20,0.2))

Muestra 2

muestra2 <- sample(u,250,replace = FALSE)
plot (muestra1, 
      main="Muestra de tamaño 250",
     xlab="Elementos de la muestra",
     ylab="uniformes(0,1)",
     col="green")

### Histograma

hist(u,col=rainbow(15,0.23))

hist(muestra1,col=rainbow(80,0.2))
